### xbrl
- balance=credit
- name=ProfitOrLoss.RealisedGainsOrLossesUnitTrustsAndManagedInvestmentVehiclesExcludingForeignExchange.Amount
- classification=baf/bafpr/bafpr2.02.06
- period=duration
